quran[31]{c,v,t}:
  1,1,"Ccekôan i Öebbi, Mass imavalen"
  1,2,Aênin Ipêunun
  1,3,Agellid n wass iqeîîiyen
  1,4,"D Keçç ay naâbed, d Keçç ay nepper d Amâ²iwen"
  1,5,Awi ya$ d ubrid iweqmen
  1,6,"Abrid n wid i T$atev; ur n wid i K isserfayen, ne$ n im$eôôqen"
  2,1,Alm
  2,2,"Appan Tezmamt, ur degs ccekk, d nnhaya i wid ipêezziben"
  2,3,"wid iumnen s tbavnit, ipéallan, ipseddiqen seg wayen iten N$at"
  2,4,"wid iumnen s wayen i k d irsen, akked wayen id irsen, uqbel ik, u, $ef laxeôt, nitni, pputebbten"
  2,5,"Widak, di nnhaya n Mass nnsen, widak, d isaâdiyen"
  2,6,"Wid ijehlen, s tidep, iâuva fellasen ma tnubav ten, ne$ ur ten tnubav. Ur ppamnen"
  2,7,"Isle$ Öebbi ulawen nnsen, akked imeééu$en nnsen. Irs le$yaô $ef allen nnsen. Fellasen aâaqeb abarar"
  2,8,"Ger yimdanen, llan wid iqqaôen: \"numen s Öebbi akked wass aneggaru”; nitni, ur llin d lmumnin"
  2,9,"La xedâen Öebbi akked wid iumnen. Ur xedâen siwa iman nnsen, ur faqen"
  2,10,"Aîan deg ulawen nnsen; Irna yasen Öebbi aîan. Fellasen aâaqeb aqeôêan, ilmend n wayen skiddiben"
  2,11,"Ma nnan asen: \"ur ssefsadet di tmurt\"! A d inin: \"nekwni d wid, kan, ipleqqimen"
  2,12,"Day maççi d nitni, s tidep, ay d ifessaden, maca ur faqen"
  2,13,"Ma nnan asen: \"amnet, akken umnen medden\"! A d inin: \"day a namen, akken umnen ije$lufen\"? Day maççi d nitni, s tidep, ay d ije$lufen, maca ur éôin"
  2,14,"Ma mmugren d wid iumnen, ad inin: \"numen\". Mara yilin weêêedsen, ar ccwaîen nnsen, ad inin: \"nekwni yidwen! Nekwni la nettihi kan"
  2,15,Öebbi ad Ittihi fellasen. Isnerna yasen lbwe$v nnsen; ddebdeben
  2,16,"Widak, d wid iu$en ttelfan s nnhaya; ur d issasay ssuq nnsen, ur pwanhan"
  2,17,"Tevôa yidsen am win issa$en times. Mi tnewweô ayen i s d izzin, Öebbi Iddem tafat nnsen, Iooa ten di tillas, ur pwalin"
  2,18,"Âaégen, gugmen, dre$len; ihi, nitni ur d ppu$alen s abrid"
  2,19,"Ne$ am usigna igenni, degs tillas, tirmegt, lebôaq. Pparran ivudan nnsen deg imeééu$en nnsen, mgal ssiâqat; ad nnestaôen si tmeppant. Öebbi Izzi i ijehliyen"
  2,20,"Qôib i sen iêwi lebôaq, iéôi. Yal tikelt ideg i sen icâal, ad ddun syis. Mi sen ixsi, ad êebsen. Ma ihwa yaS i Öebbi, ad asen Ikkes timesliwt akked yiéôi nnsen. Öebbi, s tidep, Izmer i yal cci"
  2,21,"A yimdanen! Âabdet Mass nnwen ikwen Ixelqen, kunwi, akked wid i kwen id izwaren, amar a pêezzbem"
  2,22,"i wen Irran tamurt d usu, igenni d lebni; id Isse$li d aman seg igenni, Issuffe$ ed yissen ppemôa, d ôôeéq i kunwi. Ihi, ur pparrat tanudda i Öebbi, u kunwi teéôam"
  2,23,"Ma tellam di ccekk, $ef wayen id Nessers ar umdan nne£, awit ed tasuôep i p icban. Neccdet ed inagan nnwen, war Öebbi, ma tessawalem tidep"
  2,24,"Ma ur tessawvem, u, war ccekk, ur tessawavem, êezzbet i tmes isseô$an imdanen, id$a$en, ippuheggan i ijehliyen"
  2,25,"Becceô wid iumnen, u xeddmen ayen ilhan, ar i nitni, leonanat, ddawat sen isaffen ppazzalen. Yal tikelt ara ppuôeéqen, si ppemôa nnsen, ad inin: \"d aya is neppuôeéq, uqbel\". Ippunefk asen i ten icban. Din, jjwao nnsen d ayen iûfan. Degsen ad wekkôen"